#: ../../E/era.rst:5
msgid "era"
msgstr "era"

#: ../../E/era.rst:7
msgid "n\\."
msgstr "名詞"

#: ../../E/era.rst:9
msgid ""
"Syn. :ref:`epoch`\\. Webster's Unabridged makes these words almost "
"synonymous, but era more often connotes a span of time rather than a point "
"in time, whereas the reverse is true for :ref:`epoch`\\. The :ref:`epoch` "
"usage is recommended."
msgstr ""
"\\ :ref:`epoch`\\ の同義語。Webster's "
"Unabridgedはこれらの語をほぼ同義としているが、eraは時間の一点というよりむしろ時間の幅を含意することが多く、\\ "
":ref:`epoch`\\ についてはその逆が当てはまる。\\ :ref:`epoch`\\ の用法が推奨される。"
